high_descs: Turn right and walk to the kitchen counter across the room.
Pick up the coffee mug that's next to the spoon.
Walk to the other side of the sink at the same counter and stop in front of the microwave.

Open the microwave door, place the mug inside of the microwave next to the eggs, close the microwave door, open the microwave door when the light goes off, take the mug out of the microwave, and close the microwave door.
Turn around, walk across the kitchen, and stop at the coffee maker that is on the counter next to the fridge on the left.
Place the mug in the coffee maker under the area that says "serve".
anns.task_desc: Warm up a mug to get it ready for coffee.

high_descs: Turn right and head towards the black cup on the counter.
Pick up the black cup from the counter.
Turn left and head towards the microwave to your right side.
Place the cup in the microwave, heat it up, and take it back out.
Turn around and head towards the coffee maker on your left.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated black cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the far right corner of the counter.
Pick up the mug from the counter.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Microwave the mug and pick it up again.
Turn around then go to the table on the left with the coffee maker.
Put the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and then forward to the counter.
Pick up the mug from the counter.
Go to the microwave on your left.
Microwave the mug and pick it up again.
Turn around and go to the table with the coffee maker on it.
Put the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee maker.
